{"tid":1624772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中資就唔搞得 共產黨搞國泰就冇問題?","createTime":"2019-10-05T04:49:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T18:20:23.000Z","uid":205707,"like":282,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"e42db73c3156ed0c9c70af70d2f2b2d3433872d5","tid":1624772,"uid":205707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:49:06.000Z","msg":"大家唔記得左共產黨點借國泰對手黎搞9香港人?<br />\n宜家唔搞佢地 遲D成條街都係中資我地就想揀都冇得揀<br />\n就好似買書咁 周圍都係3中書商 其他書商就比佢地打殘<br />\n好心大家大敵當前 就唔好掛住個光環啦<br />\n認同既話麻煩幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"f37e7a9741b1d442114b31099804a249af384be9","tid":1624772,"uid":27319,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:50:24.000Z","msg":"推 搞完之後我地講話佢地係國企 我地係反共匪唔係逢藍必反就得"},{"pid":"38a27bdd8f6d9a5524440760e7c605663d8ce369","tid":1624772,"uid":205707,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"f37e7a9741b1d442114b31099804a249af384be9","tid":1624772,"uid":27319,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:50:24.000Z","msg":"推 搞完之後我地講話佢地係國企 我地係反共匪唔係逢藍必反就得"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:53:59.000Z","msg":"平時佢地打劫香港人就得 我地扣返佢血唔明有咩問題"},{"pid":"67d2393588871364b0489bd9f7612ebb487561d5","tid":1624772,"uid":230104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:55:18.000Z","msg":"果40個人型物體呢？"},{"pid":"0b7c35114f700df43aca893bba43e92577061f05","tid":1624772,"uid":60872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:57:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf4fb1f36fbc3940e4c6c93cca21d65bab56805f","tid":1624772,"uid":144001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:59:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46804e84ca20e503e696bea8f14f5014e8597257","tid":1624772,"uid":205707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:32:27.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"5c08044b0a89ab945902f36b9bb38c58f171ca94","tid":1624772,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"